name: Crypto Girl H.01
description:
This work is a pure digital creation.
This woman is part of my news series called the « crypto girls » in relation to the field of digital art and NFT. All of my crypto girls represent the power of women that can be expressed in their beauty, agility, strength and cleverness. The iconic reference to super-heros and science-fiction is a markup of our times as my art is directly influenced by my youth culture. I remember learning the values of love and hate, hope and despair through cartoons and comic-books.
